name: Jaclyn Jennetten
text: This is an amazing place. Unfortunately it is temporarily (as far as I know) closed. The amazing owner passed away.    I cannot add temporarily closed to the hours, so I added its closed for the week until the family, friends and patrons can pay their respects. I will continue to do so until we know if his pizza legacy will continue.

name: Stefan Zimmerman
text: This place is unquestionably one of the tastiest place in the neighborhood. Whenever I come to this place I am incredibly satisfied. They always keep their very high  level service and the highest level of dishes  they provide. You definitely will enjoy this this restaurant. Highly  recommended.

name: Alec Earp
text: The food tastes great, but so far I'm 0/2 for actually getting everything I ordered. Would not recommend ordering delivery from here, and you should carefully check everything they give you if you order takeout.

name: Age Jasso
text: I am SOOO glad to find another Jet's pizza!! The one in my area closed down. This pizza is so addicting!!! It's so delicious, if you haven't tried it GO!! We order extra just so we can reheat it and have it the next day too! Love you Jet's!!

name: Julie Cox
